{"tid":2517925,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：皇馬一切都靠賓施馬","createTime":"2021-05-05T15:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:17:24.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1069b942d4914826afb26e54c775a6c195fb6b6","tid":2517925,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r-pyykG2cKcBOam9s_sjigJeDXc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P6662PKGABB5PHHBEEX4UOG4NE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr-pyykG2cKcBOam9s_sjigJeDXc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP6662PKGABB5PHHBEEX4UOG4NE.jpg&h=ad77e04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫格：本澤馬水平下降后 皇馬所有控球都是無用功<br />\n<br />\n在貝因體育的節目中，名帥溫格指出了皇馬在歐冠上的問題。<br />\n<br />\n  溫格表示：「本澤馬在對切爾西的上半場表現不錯，但下半場表現十分平庸。他前4次觸球都丟掉了皮球。皇馬的一大錯誤是他們的控球都是無效的。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我沒看到皇馬哪位球員有機會進入禁區，或者帶球后完成最後一傳。在這樣的情況下，球隊決定一切都靠本澤馬，不過在他水準下降后，皇馬的所有控球都做了無用功。」<br />\n<br />\n  溫格還指出了皇馬一大不足，「皇馬有水準，但缺少有深度的帶球，這在現代足球里非常重要。」"},{"pid":"1d4366d9efd423b11ff299786f42a7a061eb8a95","tid":2517925,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"雲格就認為雖然勒索案令人震驚，不過認為賓施馬不應被排除在國家隊之外：「賓施馬之所以未獲徵召並非因為他的能力問題，在我而言，賓施馬100%值得參加今夏的歐國盃賽事。他有能力為任何國家隊效力，只是因為一個非體育問題才令到他無法入選國家隊。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今季賓施馬為皇馬上陣41場並攻入28球，在基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）離開皇馬後就擔起球隊的入球重任，雲格為此亦大讚這名法國前鋒：「作為一位正選球員，他已經為皇馬上陣超過十年，而且他一直以來的入球紀錄也非常好。」"},{"pid":"2d43c1c14e3c1766a6a6c96c49a0f30e6030675a","tid":2517925,"uid":167509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"爺爺識貨，睇開F1"},{"pid":"80510d46841751bd7dfc58056f016beb1146d3f2","tid":2517925,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d43c1c14e3c1766a6a6c96c49a0f30e6030675a","tid":2517925,"uid":167509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"爺爺識貨，睇開F1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f30468870a36abc842650c1c450c1a01f03469","tid":2517925,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5e31806aae378754fc8b1b00959adb6c65cbab","tid":2517925,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d43c1c14e3c1766a6a6c96c49a0f30e6030675a","tid":2517925,"uid":167509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T15:51:46.000Z","msg":"爺爺識貨，睇開F1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"但教波用基佬"},{"pid":"aef04ecec12dad2f33cff81b98cf7bb77a26b7de","tid":2517925,"uid":295958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"離開左阿之後好似精神番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}